text: Janice Sarich (April 26, 1958February 26, 2021) was a Canadian politician. She was a member of the Progressive Conservative. Sarich was born in Edmonton, Alberta. She was a member of the Legislative Assembly of Alberta from 2008 until 2015. Sarich died on February 26, 2021 from cancer in Edmonton, aged 62. ==References== Category:1958 births Category:2021 deaths Category:Cancer deaths in Canada Category:Politicians from Edmonton
